lzh_formatted:
  title: 讀史
  author: 柳淑
  language: lzh
  text: 讀罷殘篇秋夜深。凄然吊古又悲今。廢興千載無窮事。多少英雄未了心。
korean:
  title: 독사
  author: 유숙
  language: kor
  text: |-
    묵은 책 읽고 나니 가을밤이 깊었구나
    처연히 옛날을 조상하고 지금을 슬퍼한다
    천재의 흥하고 망한 무궁한 일
    얼마나 영웅들이 마음 펴지 못했나
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0240_010_0910&viewSync=OT
english:
  title: Reading History
  author: Yu Suk
  language: eng
  text: |-
    I close the worn pages as autumn night deepens.
    I grieve for the ancients and lament the present age.
    Thousands of years of rise and fall—an endless tale—
    How many heroes died with their aspirations unfulfilled.
  footnotes:
    - The poem reflects on the cyclical nature of history and the tragedy of unrealized ambitions, a common theme in Korean classical poetry.
